data.description: Beautiful 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home with Study/Den!  We are delighted to present this charming property that could be your next dream home! Nestled in a serene Ridgemont community, this residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality.    Key Features:    - 3 bedrooms, each providing a cozy and private retreat.  - 2 well-appointed bathrooms for your convenience.  - A versatile study/den space, ideal for a home office or creative studio.  - Thoughtfully designed interior with ample natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  - Modern kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, cabinets and a split floorpan leaving space perfect for culinary enthusiasts.  - Spacious living areas, perfect for entertaining family and friends.  - The roof and AC ducts were replaced in 2020. The lot is on a cul-de-sac and is fully fenced with privacy panels, plenty of space to entertain.  - Beautifully landscaped outdoor space, providing a peaceful escape.  This property is not just a house; it's an opportunity to create lasting memories and build a life in a wonderful community.   Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the magic of this exceptional property.
